title: View a lasting power of attorney

heading_context: View a lasting power of attorney
chunks.html_content:
You can use this service to:

  • view a summary of a lasting power of attorney (LPA)
  • check whether an LPA is valid
  • check who the attorneys are on an LPA
chunks.plain_content:
View a lasting power of attorney
You can use this service to:

  view a summary of a lasting power of attorney (LPA)
  check whether an LPA is valid
  check who the attorneys are on an LPA

heading_context: View a lasting power of attorney
chunks.html_content: You can only use this service for an LPA registered in England or Wales.
chunks.plain_content:
View a lasting power of attorney
You can only use this service for an LPA registered in England or Wales.

heading_context: View a lasting power of attorney
chunks.html_content:
You’ll need an LPA access code. You can get it from the donor or an attorney named on the LPA.

If they cannot get an access code, they’ll need to show the paper LPA to you instead.
